            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avio</ex></expan> Magniano protectori con<lb break="no" n="2"/>pari carissimo Severa de proprio <lb n="3"/>hunc sarcofagum conparabit <lb n="4"/>eundem solidis XV tantum et se in <lb n="5"/>eodem una cum filia sua condi <lb n="6"/>permisit si quis vero tem<expan><ex>p</ex><abbr>taverit</abbr></expan> <lb n="7"/>in eodem sar&amp;lt;c=T&amp;gt;ofago ponere <lb n="8"/>aliut <note>sic</note> corpus inferet fisci viri<lb break="no" n="9"/>bus auri pondo duo 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Sarkophagkasten.</p>
            </div>
